strings.Value: "Wait a bit. I have an urgent matter to attend to."
{n}By the Capital, Octavia approaches, holds you close and whispers,{/n} "I want you."
"Now, and tomorrow, and always... But especially now!"
{n}She grabs your hand, and almost runs with you to the castle.{/n}
"Ha, Your Highness... Since when is love not a matter of national importance?"
